## Release checklist (maintainer discipline, extended from v0.4.3)

A version bump MUST land in one commit with:
1. `== vX.Y.Z ==` section in ANCHORS.txt, green `verify_anchors.py`;
2. regenerated `vectors.json` (freshness gate), green conformance + property suites;
3. README.md "Current" line updated;
4. CHANGELOG entry stating whether published vectors changed, and why.

